OL,3,COfcom fines GB News #100,000 over
OL,4,CRishi Sunak interview
OL,6,FOfcom has fined GB News #100,000 for
OL,7,F"breaking due impartiality rules"
OL,8,Ffollowing an interview with former
OL,9,Fprime minister Rishi Sunak earlier
OL,10,Fthis year.
OL,12,FThe media watchdog began an
OL,13,Finvestigation into GB News three days
OL,14,Fafter the airing of a programme on
OL,15,FFebruary 12, titled People's Forum:
OL,16,FThe Prime Minister, which saw Sunak
OL,17,Fanswer questions from a studio
OL,18,Faudience and a presenter.
