OL,6,FGB News chief executive Angelos
OL,7,FFrangopoulos says that the channel is
OL,8,Fchallenging the Ofcom ruling in the
OL,9,Fcourts, which they say is
OL,10,F"unnecessary, unfair and unlawful".
OL,12,FIn a statement, Ofcom said: "We
OL,13,Fconcluded that the then prime
OL,14,Fminister, Rishi Sunak, had a mostly
OL,15,Funcontested platform to promote the
OL,16,Fpolicies and performance of his
OL,17,FGovernment in a period preceding a UK
OL,18,Fgeneral election, in breach of Rules
OL,19,F5.11 and 5.12 of the Broadcasting Code.
