OL,6,F"Given the seriousness and repeated
OL,7,Fnature of this breach, Ofcom has
OL,8,Fimposed a financial penalty of
OL,9,F#100,000 on GB News Limited. We have
OL,10,Falso directed GB News to broadcast a
OL,11,Fstatement of our findings against it,
OL,12,Fon a date and in a form determined by
OL,13,Fus.
OL,15,F"GB News is challenging our original
OL,16,Fbreach decision in this case by
OL,17,Fjudicial review, which we are
OL,18,Fdefending. Ofcom will not enforce this
OL,19,Fsanction decision until those
OL,20,Fproceedings are concluded."
