OL,6,FThe statement continued: "We have
OL,7,Fbelieved from the very start the
OL,8,FPeople's Forum was an important piece
OL,9,Fof public interest programming, and
OL,10,Fthat appropriate steps were taken to
OL,11,Fensure due impartiality and compliance
OL,12,Fwith the Broadcasting Code.
OL,14,F"It was designed to allow members of
OL,15,Fthe public to put their own questions
OL,16,Fdirectly to leading politicians."
